titleNullable: YOLOv8 torso detections over BOORU CHARS
descriptionNullable:
This dataset holds results of batch [torso component detector](https://github.com/aperveyev/booru_yolo) runs over bunches of art data :
[BOORU CHARS 2021](https://nyaa.si/view/1384820)
[BOORU CHARS 2015](https://nyaa.si/view/1468367)
[BOORU CHARS 2022](https://nyaa.si/view/1547662)
[BOORU CHARS 2023](https://nyaa.si/view/1740396) also direct URL catalog there
[E621 via TBIB furry](https://nyaa.si/view/1584978)

Data structure (tab separated text) : 
* booru+fid - image ID
* batch_id - model name
* obj - object number inside model
* oid - object ID unique within image (some hash)
* prob - probability
* x, y, w, h - bounbox 
* oup - "upper" OID (head for bust level, bust for belly level)
* odn - "down" OID
* oxx - XX model OID for PP model object resided within
* ar - aspect ratio (width/height) for processed image, use it to define whether initial image was cropped
* oname - full object name for convenience

Results instances :
- **yolov8s_xx09.tsv** (11.2023) for models AA09 + PP09 (baseline)
- **yolov8s_xx10.tsv** (01.2024) for models AA10 + PP09 (outdated, dropped)
- **yolov8s_xx11.tsv** (02.2024) for models AA11 + AS03
